-- Template Variables to Replace:
-- {{RESOURCE_NAME}} - The name of your resource
-- {{AUTHOR_NAME}} - Your name or organization
-- {{VERSION}} - Version number (e.g., '1.0.0')
-- {{DESCRIPTION}} - Brief description of what the resource does
-- {{REPOSITORY_URL}} - GitHub or other repository URL

-- Common Dependencies:
-- 'es_extended' - ESX Framework
-- 'qb-core' - QB-Core Framework
-- 'mysql-async' - MySQL database connector
-- 'oxmysql' - Modern MySQL connector
-- 'menuapi' - Menu system
-- 'progressbar' - Progress bar system
-- 'mythic_notify' - Notification system
-- 'interact-sound' - Sound system

-- File Organization Tips:
-- /client/ - Client-side Lua scripts
-- /server/ - Server-side Lua scripts
-- /shared/ - Shared Lua scripts
-- /config/ - Configuration files
-- /html/ - NUI files (HTML, CSS, JS)
-- /data/ - Game data files (meta files)
-- /stream/ - Streaming files (models, textures)
-- /locales/ - Language files
-- /sql/ - Database schema files